videos.description: Virginia's Jack Salt gets the ball in the post and sinks the tough layup for the chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Salt converts layup for and-1 chance

videos.description: Hampton's Jermaine Marrow drives to the paint and converts the contested layup in the first half.
videos.headline: Marrow sinks tough layup

videos.description: Virginia's De'Andre Hunter hauls in the offensive rebound and converts the tough shot in the paint.
videos.headline: Hunter nails contested shot for 3-point chance

videos.description: Virginia's Ty Jerome takes it to the paint and drains the tough one-handed layup late in the first half.
videos.headline: Jerome converts tough lefty layup

videos.description: Virginia's De'Andre Hunter drives down the paint and converts the tough last-second layup.
videos.headline: Hunter beats the buzzer on contested layup

videos.description: Virginia's Isaiah Wilkins dishes the ball to Mamadi Diakite cutting to the basket for the loud dunk in the second half.
videos.headline: Wilkins finds Diakite for the emphatic slam

videos.description: Virginia's Nigel Johnson finds Kyle Guy cutting to the corner for the 3-pointer in the second half.
videos.headline: Guy knocks down corner 3 off inbound

videos.description: Virginia's De'Andre Hunter drives to the basket and sinks the contested layup for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Hunter finishes tough layup for and-1 opportunity

videos.description: Virginia's Nigel Johnson splits through the defense and lofts a pass up to Jay Huff for the alley-oop slam in the second half.
videos.headline: Johnson connects with Huff for the alley-oop finish

videos.description: Hampton's Charles Wilson-Fisher grabs the offensive rebound and sinks the contested shot for an and-1 opportunity.
videos.headline: Wilson-Fisher finishes putback for 3-point chance

videos.description: Following the block from Virginia's Marco Anthony, De'Andre Hunter goes coast-to-coast and converts the emphatic dunk in the second half.
videos.headline: Anthony's rejection sets up Hunter's loud slam
